org.semanticweb.vlog4j.core.model.implementation

Class TermFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.semanticweb.vlog4j.core.model.implementation.TermFilter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TermVisitor<Void>

    public class TermFilter
extends Object
implements TermVisitor<Void>
    A visitor that builds a set of terms of a specific type. It can be used to visit many terms and will only retain the ones that match the given type.
